            <fr:title text="subobject classifier of presheaves">subobject classifier of presheaves</fr:title>
            <fr:taxon>Construction</fr:taxon>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter>
            <html:p>
  The subobject classifier <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\Omega ]]></fr:tex> of presheaves can be given by a quick calculation.
  <fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[\Gamma (U, \Omega )
  \cong  \hom (\mathop {\mkern {-2mu}\text {よ}\mkern {-2mu}}(U), \Omega )
  \cong  \operatorname {Sub}(\mathop {\mkern {-2mu}\text {よ}\mkern {-2mu}}(U))]]></fr:tex>
  By definition, this is the set of <fr:link href="/forest/algm-001B/" title="sieve" uri="https://trebor-huang.github.io/forest/algm-001B/" display-uri="algm-001B" type="local">sieves</fr:link> on <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[U]]></fr:tex>, and the functorial action is the <fr:link href="/forest/algm-001C/" title="pullback of sieves" uri="https://trebor-huang.github.io/forest/algm-001C/" display-uri="algm-001C" type="local">pullback</fr:link>. For a monomorphism <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[F \hookrightarrow  G]]></fr:tex>, an element <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[s \in  \Gamma (U, G)]]></fr:tex> is sent to the sieve consisting of arrows <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f : V \to  U]]></fr:tex> such that the restriction along <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f]]></fr:tex> is included in <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[F]]></fr:tex>.
</html:p>
          </fr:mainmatter>
        </fr:tree>
